{"tid":1494782,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打自我設防 比左個監獄自己","createTime":"2019-08-21T19:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T19:20:13.000Z","uid":5205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ada85b65736658866bc57c2b3cfa8b4c1a7d19c","tid":1494782,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:03:38.000Z","msg":"一直都唔想走出去"},{"pid":"c1215f5bbad595f71cd39bb4517423181ea1eb89","tid":1494782,"uid":35484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:04:21.000Z","msg":"大家幾時先肯行動升級搞機場？<br />\n搞機場唔單只係搞到香港經濟，亦搞到全世界經濟<br />\n有機場巴絲亦指出，停飛一日全世界要2,3日善後<br />\n大家幾時先肯齊心搞呀？<br />\n唔係搞一日就算 係要成日搞<br />\n港共想攬炒唔志在香港蝕少少 但你覺得咁多受影響既外國公司想唔想蝕？<br />\n全世界陪葬既時候，你覺得啲大國會唔會出聲？<br />\n<br />\n重點係癱瘓機場交通，唔係塞爆機場入面<br />\n空管巴絲返唔到工，航班升降效率低左就會開始delay/cancel架喇"},{"pid":"7b8a77bee2b25ba90be3b662354edc6b45beb270","tid":1494782,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:05:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3f59c50cfbaf2d24871407526be7393483e85bc","tid":1494782,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:19:44.000Z","msg":"一方面覺得要打先有大啲贏面，但一諗到屋企人(佢地淺黃，見親勇武場面都係叫散水)擔心而且自己心理同生理質素唔夠強，就好似困住左自己咁樣最多做哨/人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b21beee0431a6e56347593feb1fa73ae6b03195","tid":1494782,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T19:20:13.000Z","msg":"幫手簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愛國既中國人做咩要o係海外留學<br />\n中國既學校唔好咩？<br />\n推到愛國中國人返中國讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests\" da